Extract and run UMPlayerPortable.
Target (umplayer.exe) executed by launcher as user privileges, write ExecAsAdmin=true in UMPlayerPortable.ini to execute as administrator privileges.
Language is set on startup according Windows localization (if lang-file is available), if you don't want: edit UMPlayerPortable.ini with UserDefaultLang=false.
You can pass additional commandline parameter entries into target (umplayer.exe): edit UMPlayerPortable.ini with AdditionalParameters=insert parameters here.
Screenshots saved in Screenshots, write PortableScreenshots=false in UMPlayerPortable.ini if you want to change path.
Recordings saved in Recordings, write PortableRecordings=false in UMPlayerPortable.ini if you want to change path.
Settings of installed UMPlayer should be preserved.
